Description
Century Media was created in 1988 by Despair's vocalist Robert Kampf to release their History of Hate album.
The first bands signed to Century Media where Liar, Crows, Poltergeist and Rumble Militia, however they couldnt get much success in the scene back then; although those efforts allowed Century Media to begin working with other european underground acts like Asphyx, Morgoth, Unleashed, Grave and Tiamat.
